## 1.5ct Natural Cushion Cut Diamond: Blue Nile Prices

Natural 1.5ct GIA cushion diamonds represent one of the diamond market's most significant price inflection points. The jump from natural 1ct cushion ($1,891–$2,265 for G-VS1 to F-VVS2 Ideal quality) to natural 1.5ct cushion (~$6,500–$12,000 for the same quality range) is not linear — it is exponential.

[![Cushion cut diamond halo engagement ring white gold four-prong](https://ion.bluenile.com/sets/Jewelry/Photoshoot/Bluenile/BrioPackshotBox/Rings/501410/501410_M1_CSH_DIM_wht_0100CT_W_Box5_003_1600X1600.jpg)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings?ShapeID=Cushion&a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)

