The 1.5ct lab grown cushion is where lab economics become genuinely compelling — not just moderately attractive. The $1,422 IGI E-VVS2 lab cushion versus the ~$6,500 natural GIA G-VS1 cushion represents a $5,000+ saving for a stone that is chemically and optically identical, has similar or better quality grades, and delivers the same 7.5mm face-up presence.

