## Final Verdict: Which 1.5ct Cushion Ring Is Right for You?

**Buy the [IGI 1.5ct E-VVS2 Excellent Cushion Modified at $1,422](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/28961887?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) if:** You want the strongest value in the entire cushion cluster. E colour, VVS2 clarity, Excellent cut, 1.5ct face-up presence, crushed ice modified brilliant pattern, $1,422 total stone cost. Verify the HD video shows crushed ice, confirm the cert reads "Cushion Modified," and set it in rose gold pavé for the most popular 1.5ct cushion combination under $3,000 total ring cost.

**Buy the [IGI 1.5ct E-VVS1 Ideal Cushion Modified at $1,854](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/25261211?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) if:** You specifically want Ideal cut and the VVS1 certificate tier matters for documentation or sentimental purposes. The visible quality difference between VVS2 and VVS1 at 1.5ct is zero. The $432 premium is a certificate decision, not a visual quality decision.

**Buy the [GIA 1.5ct D-IF Ideal Cushion Modified at $2,909](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/26961413?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) if:** You want GIA certification with D colour and Internally Flawless clarity on a lab stone — for insurance documentation, gift purposes, or personal preference for the GIA brand. At $2,909, this is still less than half the cost of a natural 1.5ct G-VS1 while delivering strictly superior grades on paper.

**Buy the GIA 1.5ct G-VS1 Natural Ideal Cushion Modified at ~$6,500 if:** You have a clear, examined preference for natural origin and have confirmed this preference honestly against the lab alternative. G-VS1 Ideal at 1.5ct is the natural sweet spot: near-colourless in warm metal, eye-clean clarity, Ideal cut, GIA certification. [Browse current natural 1.5ct GIA cushion inventory on Blue Nile](https://www.bluenile.com/diamonds/cushion-cut-diamonds?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) and filter by cushion shape and 1.5ct carat weight.

